markets and what we don't know, but I will
tell ya the one thing that I am absolutely

00:21:02.080 --> 00:21:12.210
certain of. And the one thing I'm absolutely
certain of is the lower the costs charged

00:21:12.210 --> 00:21:18.299
by the purveyor of the investment service,
